  "prompt": "PLAN-GATE PROTOCOL ACTIVE. Algo-trader-architect investigation 2026-05-14 found pattern_stats writer race: update_pattern_stats_from_closed_trades (learning.py:5147, time-decay corrected) and sync_realized_stats (realized_stats_sync.py:40, raw realized) write to the same scan_patterns columns. Last writer wins. Pattern 585 currently shows raw (83/34.9%) instead of corrected (87/39.8%). Fix: split into corrected_* + raw_realized_* columns, make every gate read corrected only.\n\nREAD IN ORDER:\n  1. CLAUDE.md\n  2. docs/STRATEGY/PROTOCOL.md\n  3. docs/STRATEGY/COWORK_ADVISOR_BRIEF.md\n  4. docs/STRATEGY/QUEUED/f-evidence-fidelity-architecture-2026-05-14.md (parent)\n  5. docs/STRATEGY/QUEUED/f-canonical-outcome-layer.md (THIS task)\n  6. docs/STRATEGY/NEXT_TASK.md\n  7. app/services/trading/learning.py (lines 5147+ - update_pattern_stats_from_closed_trades, the corrected writer)\n  8. app/services/trading/realized_stats_sync.py (lines 40+ - sync_realized_stats, the raw writer)\n  9. app/services/trading/promotion_gate.py + realized_ev_gate.py + cpcv_adaptive_gate.py + auto_trader.py + pattern_quality_score.py (readers to update)\n  10. app/migrations.py (find next free migration ID)\n\nDELIVER (per brief):\n  D1. Migration N+1 adds 8 columns: corrected_trade_count, corrected_win_rate, corrected_avg_return_pct, raw_realized_trade_count, raw_realized_win_rate, raw_realized_avg_return_pct, corrected_stats_updated_at, raw_realized_stats_updated_at\n  D2. learning.py update_pattern_stats_from_closed_trades dual-writes BOTH corrected_* AND legacy {trade_count, win_rate, avg_return_pct}\n  D3. realized_stats_sync.py writes ONLY raw_realized_* (never touches legacy)\n  D4. Reader updates in 5 files (promotion_gate, realized_ev_gate, cpcv_adaptive_gate, auto_trader, pattern_quality_score) - read corrected_* explicitly\n  D5. scripts/canonical-outcome-backfill.ps1 - one-shot, -DryRun default, kill switch via scripts/canonical-outcome-backfill-stop.flag\n  D6. tests/test_canonical_outcome_layer.py - race test (fire both writers, verify legacy column unchanged at corrected value, verify raw_realized_* + corrected_* both populated)\n  D7. docs/STRATEGY/CC_REPORTS/2026-05-14_canonical-outcome-layer.md\n\nMark NEXT_TASK DONE. Commit + push. Run tests with TEST_DATABASE_URL=postgresql://chili:chili@localhost:5433/chili_test.\n\nCONSULT GATE (1 item):\n  When corrected vs raw disagree by >20%, audit alert or shadow-log? Brief default: shadow-log only; alert at >50% delta. Surface in consult.\n\nHARD CONSTRAINTS:\n  - Legacy columns stay populated (mapped to corrected_*) - no consumer breaks at merge\n  - Migration is additive only - no drops, no column-type changes\n  - Backfill is -DryRun default, idempotent, kill switch\n  - No autotrader / venue / broker behavior change at merge\n  - TEST_DATABASE_URL must end in _test\n  - Plan-gate active. Escalate ONLY for unstated deviations."
